@startuml
!include ../plantuml-theme.iuml
left to right direction

title 图 2.4 会话交互与文档服务用例图

actor "普通用户" as User

rectangle "会话交互与文档服务模块" {
  usecase "开启新会话" as UC_NewSession
  usecase "实时增量呈现" as UC_Stream
  usecase "返回完成状态" as UC_Done
  usecase "历史会话回读" as UC_History
  usecase "分页读取历史" as UC_Pagination
  usecase "查看文件列表" as UC_FileList
  usecase "预览文本内容" as UC_Preview
  usecase "生成安全下载链接" as UC_Download
}

User --> UC_NewSession
User --> UC_History
User --> UC_Pagination
User --> UC_FileList
User --> UC_Preview
User --> UC_Download

UC_NewSession .> UC_Stream : <<include>>
UC_NewSession .> UC_Done : <<include>>

legend bottom
这张图需要把“会话交互”和“文档服务”并列画出，
不能只剩会话生命周期管理。
endlegend
@enduml
